OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 3 Apr to Sun 12 AprFA
OL,6,Fbroad northwest to southeast split is
OL,7,Fmost likely during this period. The
OL,8,Fnorthwest is likely to be more
OL,9,Funsettled with low pressure systems
OL,10,Fmoving in at times, bringing periods
OL,11,Fof strong winds and showers or longer
OL,12,Fspells of rain. In the southeast, high
OL,13,Fpressure will have greater influence,
OL,14,Fwith more settled, drier weather as a
OL,15,Fresult. Temperatures overall are
OL,16,Flikely to be near to or slightly above
OL,17,Fnormal, but there remains the chance
OL,18,Fof some overnight frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
